    <p class="project-period">MPU Funded Project | 2023.08 - 2026.08</p>
    <p>Role: Core member, responsible for project writing and research work.</p>
    <p>Integrating GenAI chatbots into academic writing and feedback practice, exploring the application of AI in learning assessment and student interaction patterns.</p>
