  <article class="project-item">
    <h3>Trust, Emotions and Engagement While Interacting with Generative AI Output</h3>
    <p class="project-period">MPU Funded Project | 2025.07 - 2028.07</p>
    <p>Role: Core member, responsible for project writing and research work.</p>
    <p>Investigating the relationships between user trust, emotional responses, and engagement with GenAI outputs in educational and professional settings.</p>
  </article>

  <article class="project-item">
    <h3>PhD Seminar: Measuring and Analyzing Students' Emotions in Learning</h3>
    <p class="project-period">MPU Faculty of Applied Sciences | 2025.04</p>
